        "Superpowers: Strength, speed, durability, energy manipulation, telepathy, powers based on the Infinity Stones. One of the biggest threats to all reality due to a fixation on claiming and using six stones that can warp reality, Thanos the Mad Titan is a threat that no one sneezes at as he tends to smash everything in his way. Besides this, he is also famous for his relationship with the cosmic aspect of death. This Marvel villain has superpowers that very few can defeat. Weapons: Stasis Rifle, Infinity Gauntlet .",
